sec.p:
When recovery becomes more strongly constrained relative to infection growth, the system undergoes a qualitative transition from equilibrium behaviour to sustained oscillations. FigureÂ 7 presents the parameter set \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
